ed` - Stock released from reservation\n- `notification.sent` - Notification delivered\n\n**Key Design Patterns:**\n1. **Pub/Sub Pattern**: Services register event handlers and emit events\n2. **Repository Pattern**: Each module (Orders, Inventory) has a repository for data persistence\n3. **Service Layer**: Business logic encapsulated in service classes\n4. **Global Handler Registry**: EventBus maintains a module-level handler map shared across instances\n\n**Data Flow Example (Order Creation):**\n```\nOrderService.createOrder()\n  ↓ (emits ORDER_EVENTS.CREATED)\nInventoryService.handleOrderCreated()\n  ↓ (reserves stock, emits ORDER_EVENTS.STOCK_RESERVED)\nBillingService.handleStockReserved()\n  ↓ (emits ORDER_EVENTS.PAYMENT_CHARGED)\n```\n\n**Module Dependencies:**\n- OrderService → EventBus, OrderRepository, BillingService\n- InventoryService → EventBus, InventoryRepository\n- BillingService → EventBus, NotificationService\n- NotificationService (standalone)\n\n### 4. Directory Structure\n\n```\n/workspace\n├── src/\n│   ├── index.ts\n│   ├── events/\n│   │   ├── bus.ts\n│   │   └── types.ts\n│   ├── orders/\n│   │   ├── service.ts\n│   │   └── repository.ts\n│   ├── inventory/\n│   │   ├── service.ts\n│   │   └── repository.ts\n│   ├── billing/\n│   │   ├── service.ts\n│   │   └── calculator.ts\n│   └── notifications/\n│       └── service.ts\n├── tests/ (5 test files)\n├── package.json\n├── tsconfig.json\n├── vitest.config.ts\n└── .eslintrc.cjs\n```\n\n**Total: 10 source files + 5 test files + 4 config files**"}],"totalDurationMs":26681,"totalTokens":22835,"totalToolUseCount":18,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":701,"cache_read_input_tokens":21174,"output_tokens":960,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":701,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[]}}}
